metadata.name: SuzeQ 1
metadata.description: This photorealistic portrait was inspired by my friend in Tulsa, Suze, and by her great love of her pet cats. I have known Suze for over two years now, and we chat briefly via teleconference almost every day. I hope that we can meet in person soon.  This piece very accurately depicts her youthful spirit. The piece was created using AI, with additional editing using Adobe Illustrator and Photoshop.
